episode_summary: In this episode, Jeff Biebuyck shares insights on leveraging technology and AI in real estate, the importance of mindfulness and learning from failures, and strategies for building a successful team. He discusses how to navigate market challenges, particularly in luxury markets, and the value of building strong local networks for lead generation and referrals.
